                                            they might date either to the first or the second use or even after them.
                                            The base was slightly re-cut at right after its second use. The estimated original width of the base
                                            can be inferred from the layout and was about 1.01
                                        (present dimensions <dimensions>
                                            <width>0.87</width>
                                            <height>0.29</height>
                                            <depth>0.62</depth>
                                        </dimensions>).</p>
